---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ApopTosis AI — Business">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-garamond mb-8 text-center text-prime-gold">ApopTosis AI — Business</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
      Structured for renewal, not growth at all costs. Like streams that flow and renew, not dams that hoard.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="p-8 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">Revenue Streams</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm italic">Renewal streams that sustain without exploiting</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg">
          <li>Subscriptions to PrimeFlux-Ai runtime ($99/month for pro features)</li>
          <li>Royalties from QuantaCoin transactions (1% on alignment proofs)</li>
          <li>Consulting for ethical AI governance (custom PrimeFlux integrations)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-8 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-prime-gold">Partnerships</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm italic">Cooperation over competition</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg">
          <li>xAI for networkless intelligence deployments</li>
          <li>Open-source for researchers (PrimeFlux math on GitHub)</li>
          <li>Licensing PrimeFlux for industries (finance, defense, education)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="p-8 border border-prime-gold/30 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          ApopTosis AI LLC is a Series LLC in Cheyenne, Wyoming — designed to prune and renew. 
          We don't sell data. We don't lock users. We build systems that serve humanity.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Like a garden that renews itself, our business model flows from cooperation: 
          when PrimeFlux-Ai helps you RESEARCH (explore), REFINE (evolve), RELATE (connect), 
          we both grow — not at each other's expense, but in symbiosis.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-prime-gold text-prime-blue px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-opacity-80 transition-colors inline-block">
        Partner with Us
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16 py-8 border-t border-prime-gold/30">
      <p class="text-2xl font-garamond italic text-prime-gold">
        This is not to win.<br>This is to cooperate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
